/* Table: "C_RSAttributeCode" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "C_RSAttributeCode"
(
"AttributeID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"AttributeCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"AttributeName" NVARCHAR2(100),
"Enable" INTEGER,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_C_RSATTRIBUTECODE primary key ("AttributeID")
);

comment on table "C_RSAttributeCode" is
'A03：实测面积
A06：空间信息
A07：图纸面积
';

comment on column "C_RSAttributeCode"."Enable" is
'1：启用
0：停用';
